io.github.ddimitrov.nuggets

Interface ThrowingRunnable

  • Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface ThrowingRunnable
    Functional interface for a void, parameterless lambda. Same as Runnable, but can throw exceptions.
    See Also:
    Exceptions.rethrow(ThrowingRunnable, Object), Exceptions.rethrow(ThrowingRunnable)
